        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "To show this, note that if a, b is a pair of adjacent num- bers and c, d is another pair (read in the same order around the circle) with a < d and b > c, then the seg- ment from b to c can be reversed, increasing the sum by",
        "bbox": [
